  "title": "Sales Support Assistant (Order Processing) Contract",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a US MNC in manufacturing industry.</strong><br /><br /><strong>Location: Tuas area</strong><br /><strong>Working Hour: Monday - Friday, 8.30am - 5.30pm</strong><br /><strong>Contract Duration: February 2026 - May 2026</strong><br /><br /><strong>Duties of Sales Support Assistant:</strong></p><ul><li>Process and manage sales orders accurately and in a timely manner, including order entry, updates, and documentation.</li><li>Coordinate with customers on order status, delivery schedules, forecasts, and inventory levels.</li><li>Liaise with internal teams (Production, Planning, Purchasing, Warehouse) to ensure smooth order fulfilment and timely delivery.</li><li>Prepare shipping documents, invoices, and related paperwork for deliveries, amendments, and cancellations.</li><li>Handle customer enquiries and complaints, and work with QA to ensure issues are resolved promptly.</li><li>Maintain Bills of Materials (BOM), records, and documentation, ensuring proper filing and internal controls.</li><li>Provide administrative support to the Sales team and follow up on customer payments.</li><li>Assist with monthly reporting, stock counts, freight coordination, and customs-related documentation.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in customer service and order processing.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</li></ul>",
